between the traditional era

00:21:58.330 --> 00:21:59.600 align:middle line:90%
and the metaphysical era.

00:21:59.600 --> 00:22:00.400 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:22:00.400 --> 00:22:03.070 align:middle line:84%
>> How do you-- do you see
that as a valid distinction?

00:22:03.070 --> 00:22:05.660 align:middle line:90%
