religious, the metaphysical,

00:22:08.980 --> 00:22:10.280 align:middle line:90%
and the scientific.

00:22:10.280 --> 00:22:11.080 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:22:11.080 --> 00:22:19.570 align:middle line:84%
>> So the metaphysical, he in
his view of progress felt was

00:22:19.570 --> 00:22:22.150 align:middle line:84%
better than the religious,
but it was inferior

00:22:22.150 --> 00:22:23.150 align:middle line:90%
to the scientific.

00:22:23.150 --> 00:22:23.950 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:22:23.950 --> 00:22:29.050 align:middle line:84%
>> So the only world view
that his scheme allowed is

00:22:29.050 --> 00:22:33.760 align:middle line:84%
the scientific world view,
but as we know or are coming

00:22:33.760 --> 00:22:37.820 align:middle line:84%
to know, it can deal only
with the physical universe.

00:22:37.820 --> 00:22:38.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

